Chrome / Firefox Extensions
- Bump version, run `lb-build` and upload to each portal.

Electron
- `lb-electron` to copy files from main repo, bump version, `npm start` to test and `npm run dist` to create executables (for each OS).
- Use git-bash in Windows

Mobile
- `yarn bundle-ios` to create assets file for IOS, `yarn bundle-android` to create assets file for Android.
- XCode bump version, clean build folder and archive.
- Android Studio, run gradle task to build signed APK.
